page.title: 16ERIC,ANNAN
page.content: I wake up about 7.00am.I get dressed and washed then have my breakfast.I leave my house at 8.30am to go to school. I reach school about 8.45am.At 9.00am I go into school.In the morning I usually get maths.At 10.30am we have playtime.I usually play football with my friends.When we come in I get more maths then English.At 12.30pm it is dinner break.I play football with my friends all break again.After dinner break,at 1.30pm,we get creative work.Afternoon break is at 2.30pm.When we go back into class we finish our work.We go home at 3.30pm I change and watch TV till 5.00pm.I then get my tea.After that I go out to play with my brother Colin or my friends.I go to bed at 9.30pm and am usually asleep by 10.00pm.
